v1.headline: Senior Recruiting Coordinator @ Wolt
v1.about: An energetic, resourceful and highly motivated individual, who enjoys learning new skills, getting involved in new projects and adapting to new situations. With a keen sense of humour, I thrive in a team environment and can work well on my own whilst taking on high levels of responsibility.  I remain focused under pressure and always take on duties in an enthusiastic manner and deliver within set timescales. I am motivated, punctual, approachable, trustworthy and very reliable.
